20:13.583 --> 20:19.288
We're done with it, and we're on to another 
village, and these people aren't in the

20:13.583 --> 20:19.288
construction mess anymore. And we can take 30 
years, and we aren't pestering everybody with 30

20:20.289 --> 20:28.778
years worth of construction activity around 
their ears, because we do a village at a time. They

20:29.839 --> 20:32.922
overlap, of course. So you survived the slump, 
